dataIdInfo.idPurp: Process transducer data, removing barometric pressure and linear drift, and loads the data into an SDE database. Created for internal use in the Utah Geological Survey.
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Process transducer data, removing barometric pressure and linear drift, and loads the data into an SDE database. Created for internal use in the Utah Geological Survey.

This toolbox works best with an updated version of ArcGIS Pro, and the Python Pandas library.
